N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 6208.2 - Service of petition; timeliness

State Regulations
(a) The original petition shall be served at the office of the State Board of

Elections, 40 North Pearl Street, Suite 5, Albany, NY 12207-2729, or upon any
person authorized by the State Board of Elections to receive such
service. Notes
